{"title":"Drankful Hydration MTB Waist Pack puts 1.5L on your hips, plus Stealth Pack for Enduro","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/03/drankful-hydration-mtb-waist-pack-puts-1-5l-on-your-hips-plus-stealth-pack-for-enduro/","date":1627992030000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Drankful are crowdfunding a new Hydration Hip Pack for mountain bikers, describing it as the ultimate lumbar adventure pack. A 1.5L hydration bladder with dedicated internal compartment and magnetic hose clip, an offset magnetic buckle, deployable hidden water bottle pockets and a weatherproof exterior… this MTB Hip Pack seems to have it all. There’s also the Drankful Stealth Hydration Pack designed primarily for runners, but could also serve as the ultimate pack for enduro racing, too.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"drankful hydration hip pack mountain biking waist water storage\" width=\"1400\" height=\"934\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-1068x713.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.8623953617002635\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-1068x713.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061022/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-closeup-feature-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 630w\"></a></p><p>The new Drankful Hydration Hip Pack for mountain bikers looks killer. While it may not have the most radical aesthetic, it does cram a number of clever and useful design features into a relatively small package with a weatherproof exterior.</p><p>It’s primary function is hydration of course. The Drankful 1.5 Litre hydration bladder sits inside its own dedicated compartment, with a hose extending out either side of the rider’s waist to marry with a magnetic clip on the opposite side. The clip holds it in place securely so the hose doesn’t wildly flail about as you ride over rough terrain.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets.jpg\" alt=\"drankful mtb hip pack two hidden water bottle storage pockets full size extra hydration\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-1068x711.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-631x420.jpg 631w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-1068x711.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03070000/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-hidden-water-bottle-pockets-631x420.jpg 631w\"></a></p><p>The compartment holding the hydration bladder is said to be ultra snug, leaving no room for the bladder and the water inside it to slosh about too much. That’s not the only water storage location, however. On each side of the pack are hidden elasticated pockets that can hold two full size water bottles. You might make use of these when headed out on a long adventure or gravel ride; they don’t look secure enough to hold onto the water bottles on anything too bumpy, though there is an elasticated cord you can deploy to wrap around the top of the bottle for a bit of additional security.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration.jpg\" alt=\"drankful mtb hip pack\" width=\"1200\" height=\"676\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration-