/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration-768x433.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration-1068x602.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062333/drankful-mtb-hip-pack-water-carry-hydration-746x420.jpg 746w\"></a></p><p>On each hip there is also a small zippered pocket, useful for storing items you’ll want quick, easy access to, like cash, keys or snacks. There’s also a larger pocket on the front of the main compartment where you could store a multi-tool and a phone.</p><h3>One for the Runners and Enduro Racers</h3><figure id=\"attachment_267181\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-267181\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1.jpg\" alt=\"drankful hydration pack running enduro mountain bike racing\" width=\"1024\" height=\"778\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1.jpg 1024w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1-297x226.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1-800x608.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/