umor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1-696x529.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1-553x420.jpg 553w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061104/drankful-hydration-pack-biking-hiking-running-1024x778-1-80x60.jpg 80w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-267181\">We think this could be a great solution for enduro racing, especially big mountain days where riders need to carry a first aid kit and additional supplies to be self sufficient</figcaption></figure><p>Though primarily aimed at runners, it’s easy to see that the Drankful Stealth Hydration Pack could serve enduro racers very well. While we may regularly go out on a trail ride around the local woods with the absolute bare minimum, enduro racers need to be self sufficient over the course of a race. Many of the Pros put a lot of thought into optimizing their setup to carry the food, spares and tools they might need over the course of a day’s racing.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder.jpg\" alt=\"drankful hydration pack 1.5 litre bladder\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-1068x711.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-631x420.jpg 631w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-1068x711.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061051/drankful-hydration-bladder-631x420.jpg 631w\"></a></p><p>To me, the Drankful Stealth Hydration Pack looks to be a good solution. It holds the 1.5 Litre bladder in a dedicated pocket which sits against the small of the rider’s back, said to act like a pillow. Above that is a separate storage compartment secured by a magnetic closure, where there looks to be plenty of room for a waterproof jacket, tools and spares.&nbsp;</p><figure id=\"attachment_267186\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-267186\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running.jpg\" alt=\"drankful hydration pack enduro racers pack\" width=\"1200\" height=\"676\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-800x451.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-768x433.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-1068x602.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-746x420.jpg 746w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-800x451.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-768x433.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-1068x602.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03062327/drankful-hydration-pack-mtb-running-746x420.jpg 746w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-267186\">The Drankful Stealth Hydration Pack is available in sizes S-XL, serving chest sizes of 31″ to 45″+</figcaption></figure><p>The pack is constructed a bit like a jacket, with two buckles that wrap around the wearer’s chest and waist to secure the pack close against the body to prevent unnecessary movement. On the front are two zippered pockets for those easy access items such as snacks, cash or a whistle (to call for help if you find yourself in a ditch).</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners.jpg\" alt=\"drankful hydration pack range mtb running enduro hiking\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1001\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-297x248.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-800x667.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-120x100.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-768x641.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-696x581.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-1068x891.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-503x420.jpg 503w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-297x248.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-800x667.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-120x100.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-768x641.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-696x581.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-1068x891.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03061058/drankful-hydration-hip-pack-mountain-bikers-runners-503x420.jpg 503w\"></a></p><p>The Drankful Hydration MTB Waist Pack, Stealth Hydration Pack and Runners Waist Pack (the smallest in the image above) are available for pre-order now through <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/drankfulstealth/1370319320?token=fb89e3bb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Drankful’s Kick Starter campaign</a>. Pledging $69 USD gets you the Mountain Bike Waist Pack with reservoir and drinking tube included. A pledge of $99 USD gets you the Drankful Stealth Hydration Pack. Those deals are only available on Day 1 (today, at time of writing) of the Kick Starter campaign. Shipping is expected in December of 2021.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/drankfulstealth/1370319320?token=fb89e3bb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Drankful Kick Starter Page</a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f9ce8688e352c30f0afa04085a4d21b1afacaf68adff5458a0f81d0ef8b510a2","category":"Cycling"}